### Youyu - Support Tickets
### Run this file after every change to support-ticket endpoints.
### Prerequisite: backend started with -Dspring-boot.run.profiles=seed

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@userToken = mock-1001-USER
@otherUserToken = mock-1002-USER
@adminToken = mock-9001-ADMIN
@supportToken = mock-9102-SUPPORT_AGENT
@ticketId = 6201

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# USER SUPPORT TICKETS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Create support ticket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "order",
  "subject": "Order delivery status needs help",
  "content": "The seller has not updated delivery progress. Please help me check the platform record.",
  "relatedType": "order",
  "relatedId": 8001
}

###

### List my support tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### List my open support tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets?status=open&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Read my support ticket detail
### Expected: public messages only; no internal_note messages.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Add user public reply
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "I can provide more order screenshots if needed."
}

###

### User cannot read another user's ticket - expect 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{otherUserToken}}

###

### Reject invalid ticket category - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "chat",
  "subject": "Invalid category smoke",
  "content": "Support tickets must use the closed category set."
}

###

### Reject blank user reply - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": ""
}

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# ADMIN SUPPORT TICKETS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

###

### Admin list support tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Support agent list open order tickets
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets?status=open&category=order&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}

###

### Support agent list tickets assigned to me
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets?assignedToMe=true&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}

###

### Admin search tickets by keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets?keyword=delivery&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Admin search tickets by related order id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets?keyword=8001&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}

###

### Admin ticket detail
### Expected: public_reply and internal_note messages are visible to admin.
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Admin move ticket to in_progress and assign to self
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in_progress",
  "assignToMe": true
}

###

### Admin add public reply
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageType": "public_reply",
  "content": "We are checking the order context and will update this ticket after review."
}

###

### Admin add internal note
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageType": "internal_note",
  "content": "Check report/order context only. Do not mutate order or mediation state from this ticket."
}

###

### Reject invalid status transition - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "open"
}

###

### Reject invalid message type - expect 400 BAD_REQUEST
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/support/tickets/{{ticketId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{supportToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messageType": "private_chat",
  "content": "Invalid support-ticket message type."
}
